plot: Bart takes up smoking e-cigarettes to impress Milhouse's cousin Annika while the rest of the family learns about Grampa's days in the Air Force.

Homer is arrested by the military after trying to sabotage expensive children's birthday parties and made to listen to his father recounting his days in the air force, where he broke the sound barrier and met his future wife. Bart takes up smoking electronic cigarettes to impress Milhouse's cousin, who is visiting from the Netherlands, but ultimately decides that she is not worth impressing.—don @ minifie-1
